text.tspan: DIY AIR CLEANING: MAKING A 'CORSI AIR BOX' / 'COMPARETTO CUBE'
CAN ADD THE EQUIVALENT OF ~ + 3 AIR CHANGES PER HOUR
TYPICAL ESTIMATED CADR (CLEAN-AIR DELIVERY RATE): ~ 600 CFM
EQUIVALENT ACH (AIR CHANGES PER HOUR) = CADR * 60 / ROOM_VOLUME
E.G.: FOR 30 FT x 30 FT x 10 FT ROOM, TYPICAL ESTIMATED EQUIVALENT ACH ~ + 3 ACH
(FOR COMPARISON: TYPICAL CLASSROOM ACH < 3 ACH; IDEAL ACH: 6+ )
FOR MORE BACKGROUND & REFERENCES, VISIT edgecollective.io/airbox
* Most 20" box fans -- including all those sold in CA after 2012 -- are sold with a (built-in) fuse.
